<section class="section" id="get-started">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-section">
      <h2>Be the first to try it</h2>
      <p>
        RepoMind is in active development. Drop your email and we'll let
        you know the moment you can run it on your own repos — or reach out
        if you want to be a design partner.
      </p>

      <form
        class="cta-form"
        action="https://formspree.io/f/your-form-id"
        method="POST"
      >
        <input
          type="email"
          name="email"
          placeholder="you@yourteam.com"
          required
          aria-label="Email address"
        />
        <button type="submit">Notify me</button>
      </form>
      <p class="cta-note">
        No spam, no VC updates — just a launch email. You can also
        <a href="https://github.com/adnan4k/repo_mind">star the repo</a> to
        follow along.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
